comments: Quickley (NYK) reaches across and makes contact with the ball, any additional contact to Booker's (PHX) hip is considered incidental.
Barrett (NYK) establishes himself in a screening position and is firming up when marginal contact occurs to Booker's (PHX) side.
Barrett (NYK) wraps his arm around Booker's (PHX) upper body and initiates contact that affects his FOM.
Nurkic (PHX) establishes himself in Barrett's (NYK) path and briefly clasped Barrett's arm during the screen before correcting.
Quickley (NYK) legally contests Gordon's (PHX) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Brunson (NYK) delivers contact to Booker (PHX) and dislodges him from his position.
Nurkic (PHX) turns and delivers body contact that affects Quickley's (NYK) follow-through.
Goodwin (PHX) maintains his arms within the frame of his body and slides his hands off of Barrett's (NYK) body as he defends over the pick.
Brunson (NYK) lightly brushes Booker's (PHX) arm and immediately slides his hand off.
Booker (PHX) gathers the ball on his right foot and comes to a jump stop, which is his first step and takes his second step on his right foot.
Robinson (NYK) moves alongside of Nurkic (PHX) and absorbs the marginal body contact defending Nurkic's post move.
Randle (NYK) reaches in and pulls Nurkic's (PHX) arm off the ball during his post play.
A 24 second violation is correctly assessed.
Booker (PHX) is moving alongside Brunson's (NYK) path and marginal body contact occurs at the end of Brunson's drive.
Booker (PHX) and Quickley (PHX) come together and Booker absorbs the marginal body contact on the perimeter.
Randle (NYK) is in the lane for longer than three seconds.
Robinson (NYK) establishes himself in Goodwin's (PHX) path and absorbs the contact.
Nurkic (PHX) momentarily places a collapsing forearm Brunson's (NYK) front and marginal contact occurs during Brunson's drive.
Nurkic (PHX) already in Barrett's (NYK) path and absorbs the marginal body contact.
On the dribble handoff, Goodwin (PHX) makes marginal contact with Barrett (NYK) as defends under the pick.
Randle (NYK) legally contests Booker's (PHX) jump shot attempt.
Booker (PHX) briefly grasps Quickley's (NYK) jersey off ball.
